About
-----

Basic sentry installation in a vagrant box.


Requirements
------------

Uses ansible roles defined in https://github.com/fdemmer/ansible_roles


Quickstart
----------

- Clone the repository
- Run `vagrant up`
- SSH into the box `vagrant ssh` and create initial superuser:
  `$ SENTRY_CONF=/etc/sentry /www/sentry/bin/sentry createuser`
- Enjoy sentry on http://10.10.10.100:9000
